<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Server Info</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Server Information:</h2>
  <p>Hostname: {{ ansible_hostname }}</p>
  <p>IP Address: {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
  <p>Operating System: Gentoo {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</p>
  <p>Kernel: {{ ansible_kernel }}</p>
  <p>Architecture: {{ ansible_architecture }}</p>
  <p>Deployment Time: {{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</p>
  <br>
  <strong>Your Nginx web server is running successfully!</strong><br>
  <em>Deployed with Ansible automation</em>
</body>
</html>
